General.Name: Numis Corp
General.Description: Numis Corporation Plc, through its subsidiaries, provides various investment banking services in the United Kingdom, the United States, and Ireland. The company offers investment banking services, including corporate broking, debt advisory, equity capital markets, growth capital solutions, IPOs, and mergers and acquisitions. It also provides equities services, such as research, and sales and trading. The company serves investment trusts, asset managers, private companies, private equity funds, private client fund managers, family offices, sovereign wealth funds, hedge funds, and venture capital funds. Numis Corporation Plc was incorporated in 1989 and is based in London, the United Kingdom.
